      "writtenOn": "2017-11-15T01:03:38Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u0026dbKey\n\nOtherwise some other package may do context.WithValue(..., \"db\", ...) and screw up everything.\n\n\u0026dbKey is stable unique address (being an address of a global variable). No other package will be able to reuse it (since dbKey is private variable).",
